{"tid":214110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呀嬸呀叔一出事就扮專家真係好黑人憎","createTime":"2017-04-23T14:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T14:49:21.000Z","uid":32906,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"caed1ce51d8024b14e6743500848706478a009ea","tid":214110,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"搭171 巴士入鴨脷洲橋口封左路，<br />\n一無上到橋就鬼曬咁嘈。<br />\n👴🏻司機唔識路呀！！<br />\n👵哈哈一定踩油踩過龍啦<br />\n👴🏻唔記得轉彎呀麻<br />\n👴🏻司機肯定唔係行開呢條線啦<br />\n以下先癲：<br />\n👵死喇，會車我地去邊嫁<br />\n👵洗唔洗話比司機知呀<br />\n👴🏻落去話比個司機知行錯啦<br />\n我已經幫司機解釋左<br />\n但有幾個呀嬸我解釋完比你班豬聽，你都仲要屈個司機唔識路，入唔切彎......<br />\n屌你地死撚左去啦，無撚用嫁啦，阻住香港發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c260df6686a1a4a42f53d469c6a5df11c9650c","tid":214110,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚醒你黎揸，無車牌都可以嘈生曬"},{"pid":"0eaf05e1c375f60d266c5f4fa8a3c2a4f10002a5","tid":214110,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"仲要話應該入香港仔轉線。<br />\n我屌你啦，你想遊車河呀？<br />\n一撚定係田灣最撚快不服來辯"},{"pid":"82d994edf367cb5aa6ffcddea07142e18303cd21","tid":214110,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"同網民乜撚都唔知就嘈一聲咪又差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1d4168c86c5812bb485223499060570deef616","tid":214110,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同網民乜撚都唔知就嘈一聲咪又差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d 人都唔知大個左會唔會變呢類廢中，好心呢d 人就用下腦，解釋完都仲要死撐"}]}